{"tid":2251100,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Trump: 美國司法部長巴爾 唔該你快手啲安排人去追查Hunter Biden 電腦單野","createTime":"2020-10-20T14:12:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T12:00:47.000Z","uid":204533,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"40454aba64e0eb2d43548e35696e962dbd84255a","tid":2251100,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T14:12:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span class=\"red\">President Trump on Tuesday said Attorney General William Barr needs to &ldquo;act&rdquo; and &ldquo;appoint somebody&rdquo; after nearly a dozen House Republicans urged him to tap a special counsel to investigate alleged revelations coming from a laptop purported to have belonged to Joe Biden&rsquo;s son Hunter.</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nDuring an exclusive interview with &ldquo;Fox &amp; Friends&rdquo; on Tuesday, the president criticized his Democratic opponent and Hunter Biden, saying he &ldquo;walked around like a vacuum.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;This is the laptop from hell,&rdquo; Trump said. &ldquo;<strong><span class=\"red\">Even if he didn&rsquo;t get all of this money, you can&rsquo;t go to China and have the son walk out with $1.5 billion. ... You can&rsquo;t go to Ukraine with $83,000 a month. ... You can&rsquo;t get $3.5 million from the mayor of Moscow&rsquo;s wife.</span></strong>&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">And you didn&rsquo;t have a job before your father was vice president</span></span></strong>,&rdquo; Trump continued. &ldquo;You can&rsquo;t go and go with your father and every stop you make, you pick up $1 billion.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nHe added: &ldquo;The vice president got a kickback, and everybody knows it, and they&rsquo;ve known it a long time.&rdquo;</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/politics/trump-william-barr-act-hunter-biden-business-dealings\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-william-barr-act-hunter-biden-business-dealings&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QRnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=d093ff1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-william-barr-act-hunter-biden-business-dealings&h=6619d19e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxnews.com/politics/trump-william-barr-act-hunter-biden-business-dealings</a>"},{"pid":"9a667e84e10770742e50124793ce0ab2b111fca2","tid":2251100,"uid":204533,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T14:16:08.000Z","msg":"同場加映, 琴日十一名共和黨國會議員都叫左<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/politics/house-gop-fbi-hunter-biden-laptop\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fhouse-gop-fbi-hunter-biden-laptop&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QRnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=db39b9a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fhouse-gop-fbi-hunter-biden-laptop&h=be66e8f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxnews.com/politics/house-gop-fbi-hunter-biden-laptop</a>"},{"pid":"4cb8b86726eec6426264a729dc7004c9e1346add","tid":2251100,"uid":104112,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T14:20:08.000Z","msg":"DON WICK:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yfWyKnr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyfWyKnr.gif&h=0741936f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QCk7OPw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQCk7OPw.gif&h=65c8f155&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03e63a7096d6e928eee72810004144782da7fff1","tid":2251100,"uid":33263,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4cb8b86726eec6426264a729dc7004c9e1346add","tid":2251100,"uid":104112,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T14:20:08.000Z","msg":"DON WICK:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yfWyKnr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyfWyKnr.gif&h=0